Overview
Komatireddy Raj Gopal Reddy is an Indian politician and a former Member of Legislative Assembly of Munugode of Telangana state, ex Member of Legislative Council and ex member of the 15th Lok Sabha. He was former Bharatiya Janata Party leader till October 2023. Wikipedia >
